like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T18:13:31.000Z","msg":"啱呀啱呀"},{"pid":"41dbb3b06106ae3feee879589316bcb45fee51c0","tid":2133914,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T18:19:58.000Z","msg":"m$就係垃圾"},{"pid":"e7f415b4102b5f65ff58045eb5d06adf067077b3","tid":2133914,"uid":112748,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fdf0b8e3f800330c96585a72a3f3febe4441d8a4","tid":2133914,"uid":149829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T11:02:39.000Z","msg":"公司用緊onedrive, sharedrive...<br />\n呢期WFH索性將啲file搬哂落sharedrive諗住方便攞....<br />\n我屌佢老味, D file次撚次都sync到啲又唔sync到啲<br />\n攪到我差啲唔哂啲file, 呢個file sync到, 另一個又唔得<br />\n就黎俾onedrive玩撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重新connect 繼續pending to sync, <br />\n垃圾, 垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T18:54:01.000Z","msg":"全新的 Winsows 電腦一打開，就有 OneDrive 這個軟體的存在，坦白說目前免費的雲端硬碟，Google Drive 與 Dropbox 仍然是大家比較喜愛的，而電腦一買來就粗暴安裝在系統中的 OneDrive，真的是用不太到，開機時又會跟著啟動拖慢電腦速度，雖然說可以設定不跟著系統一起啟動，但是要移除它也不是件容易的事。今天跟大家分享網路上傳出可以利用批次檔，來一鍵刪除 OneDrive 的方法，實測之後，真的可以順順的移除，文末也提供能刪除 OneDrive 的 cmd 檔讓大家可以快速取用並輕鬆移除 OneDrive 喔！<br />\n<br />\n移除 OneDive 批次檔：<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n@echo off<br />\ncls<br />\nset x86=&quot;%SYSTEMROOT%\\System32\\OneDriveSetup.exe&quot;<br />\nset x64=&quot;%SYSTEMROOT%\\SysWOW64\\OneDriveSetup.exe&quot;<br />\n<br />\necho Closing OneDrive process.<br />\necho.<br />\ntaskkill /f /im OneDrive.exe &gt; NUL 2&gt;&amp;1<br />\nping 127.0.0.1 -n 5 &gt; NUL 2&gt;&amp;1<br />\n<br />\necho Uninstalling OneDrive.<br />\necho.<br />\nif exist %x64% (<br />\n%x64% /uninstall<br />\n) else (<br />\n%x86% /uninstall<br />\n)<br />\nping 127.0.0.1 -n 5 &gt; NUL 2&gt;&amp;1<br />\n<br />\necho Removing OneDrive leftovers.<br />\necho.<br />\nrd &quot;%USERPROFILE%\\OneDrive&quot; /Q /S &gt; NUL 2&gt;&amp;1<br />\nrd &quot;C:\\OneDriveTemp&quot; /Q /S &gt; NUL 2&gt;&amp;1<br />\nrd &quot;%LOCALAPPDATA%\\Microsoft\\OneDrive&quot; /Q /S &gt; NUL 2&gt;&amp;1<br />\nrd &quot;%PROGRAMDATA%\\Microsoft OneDrive&quot; /Q /S &gt; NUL 2&gt;&amp;1<br />\n<br />\necho Removeing OneDrive from the Explorer Side Panel.<br />\necho.<br />\nREG DELETE &quot;HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\\CLSID\\{018D5C66-4533-4307-9B53-224DE2ED1FE6}&quot; /f &gt; NUL 2&gt;&amp;1<br />\nREG DELETE &quot;HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\\Wow6432Node\\CLSID\\{018D5C66-4533-4307-9B53-224DE2ED1FE6}&quot; /f &gt; NUL 2&gt;&amp;1<br />\n<br />\npause<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------"},{"pid":"8e09cfcf91f4b2891520e19a078d8de626c912f5","tid":2133914,"uid":111998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T02:00:23.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n成日Excel save 唔到,自動幫我create多個file<br />\n但係舊file 係save到既"}]}